PRECAUTION

    Note, that updating major versions of libffi (in x.y.z changing x or y)
    requires rebuilding ports like python3, llvm-toolchain, ruby, glib,
    gobject-introspection and others.

    Have revdep(1) point out potential candidates
    for rebuilds after the libffi update.

